== Getting Started with Coffee Script
  
This is a demonstration app inspired by Dr Nic's overview (see link below). It is a 
plain simple Rails 2.3.x project, without any database dependencies to showcase
CoffeeScript using jQuery UI elements in a single page.

== Links

Read Dr Nic's overview on CoffeeScript and BistroCar for Rails projects:
  http://drnicwilliams.com/2010/03/15/using-coffeescript-in-rails-and-even-on-heroku/
  
Read CoffeeScript Reference Guide:
  http://jashkenas.github.com/coffee-script/
  
Install a Textmate Bundle for CoffeeScript:
  http://github.com/jashkenas/coffee-script-tmbundle
  
Read more about jQuery and jQuery UI:
  http://jqueryui.com/docs/Getting_Started
  
Use Google's CDN to point to jQuery:
  http://code.google.com/apis/ajaxlibs/documentation/#jquery